Fall semester 2026-27: new Admissions Cycle
---
We are excited to announce that applications are now open for the Fall semester 2026-27 admissions cycle!
---
Submission Deadline:
June 30, 2026
---
Call for applications fall 2026-27
Apply here
---
Admission
---
The applications have to be submitted via the online application system (
https://e-graduate.tuc.gr
). Information about processing of personal data for the purposes of evaluation and registration, in addition to the collection of the supporting documents, can be found in Admission - School of Mineral Resources Engineering (tuc.gr)
---
Important notes:
• Applications may be submitted even with temporary omissions (such as a pending diploma certificate or diploma thesis presentation), on the condition that all requirements are fulfilled and documentation is provided before the semester begins.
• Personal interviews will be conducted for all applicants on line after an invitation from the Graduate Committee. In order to facilitate an early decision for candidates, personal interviews
